  <entry>
    <title type="html">Guide</title>
    <id>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/guide/</id>
    <link href="https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/guide/"/>
    <updated>2021-02-27T06:18:09.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="usage"> Usage</h2>
<p>After enabling, this plugin will automatically add a copy button to the bottom right corner of each code block.</p>
<p>By default, the button is only displayed on desktop mode. If you want to display this button on mobile devices, set <code>showInMobile</code> to <code>true</code>.</p>
<p>After user press the copy button, a success hint will display on the screen. The default hint duration is 2000ms, if you want to change the duration, please set <code>duration</code> in options (ms). If you want to disable the hint, set duration to <code>0</code>.</p>
<h2 id="effect"> Effect</h2>
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.js</span>
module<span>.</span>exports <span>=</span> <span>{</span>
  plugins<span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"@mr-hope/copy-code"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// your options</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div>]]></content>
